<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2610272>
    dc:description "FIGURES 83–92. Immature stages of Mesosemia walteri. 83, egg; 84, first instar; 85 first (above) and second instar (below); 86, third instar in dorsal view; 87, fourth instar in dorsal view; 88, last instar in lateral view; 89, detail of abdominal tegument in dorsal view showing dorsal setae on verrucae; 90, last instar dorsal view, note the TNOs everted (arrow); 91, prepupa in lateral view; 92 pupa in dorsal (left) and lateral (right) views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2610272/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

